  "english": [
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> With regard to <b>a nazirite who shaved</b> for the conclusion of his naziriteship, <b>and it</b> later <b>became known to him that</b> during his naziriteship <b>he was ritually impure</b> from a corpse, <b>if</b> it was <b>a known impurity,</b> i.e., people were aware of the impurity when he became impure, <b>he negates</b> his entire naziriteship. <b>And if it was ritual impurity</b> imparted by a grave <b>in the depths,</b> one that was unknown at the time, <b>he does not negate</b> his naziriteship. <b>If</b> he discovered he was impure <b>before he shaved, he negates</b> his naziriteship <b>in either case.</b>",
    "The mishna asks: <b>How</b> does one differentiate between a known and an unknown impurity? If a nazirite <b>descended to immerse in a cave, and a corpse was found floating at the mouth of the cave,</b> he is <b>impure,</b> as an openly visible corpse is a known impurity. What, then, is an impurity of the depths? This is referring to a case where the corpse <b>was found sunk into the ground of the cave</b> in such a manner that it was unknown.",
    "However, even here the circumstances of the case must be taken into account. If one <b>descended</b> not to immerse himself in the water, as he was ritually pure, but <b>to cool</b> himself, he remains <b>pure.</b> If he was impure and entered the water <b>to purify himself from the impurity from a corpse,</b> he is <b>impure.</b> The reason is that something <b>that</b> has <b>the presumptive status of impurity</b> remains <b>impure, and</b> something that has <b>the presumptive status of purity</b> is <b>pure, as there is a basis for the matter.</b> It is reasonable that items or people retain their presumptive status.",
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> The Gemara asks: <b>From where are these matters</b> derived, that there is a difference between known and unknown impurity? <b>Rabbi Eliezer said that the verse states</b> with regard to a nazirite: <b>“And if any man shall die very suddenly beside him”</b> (Numbers 6:9). The emphasis provided by the term <b>“beside him”</b> indicates <b>that</b> it is <b>clear to him</b> that he has become impure. However, one is not impure if the presence of the corpse is unknown.",
    "<b>Reish Lakish said</b> a different source: <b>The verse states</b> with regard to the Paschal offering: “Any man of you <b>who shall be ritually impure due to a corpse or on a road far away”</b> (Numbers 9:10). The word “road” is juxtaposed in the verse to the term “ritually impure,” indicating that the impurity is <b>like a road. Just as a road is in the open, so too, every</b> impurity is <b>in the open.</b> It must be a known impurity.",
    "The Gemara objects: <b>But</b> consider <b>that which we learned</b> in the <i>Tosefta</i> (<i>Zavim</i> 2:9): <b>Which is the ritual impurity</b> imparted by a grave <b>in the depths?</b> It is impurity imparted by <b>any</b> corpse <b>of which no one is aware,</b> even <b>at the end of the earth.</b> This type of impurity is permitted for both a nazirite and one who sacrifices the Paschal offering. <b>However,</b> if even <b>one</b> person <b>is aware of it,</b> even <b>at the end of the earth, this is not impurity</b> imparted by a grave <b>in the depths.</b>",
    "The Gemara states its question: <b>Granted, according to the one who says</b> that this <i>halakha</i> is derived from the verse that states that ritual impurity is <b>like a road,</b> it is <b>fine,</b> as an item known to someone in the world can be compared to a road. <b>However, according to the one who says</b> that this <i>halakha</i> is derived from the term “beside him,” i.e., it is referring <b>to</b> an impurity that is <b>clear to him, if one</b> person <b>at the</b> other <b>end of the earth is aware of</b> this impurity, <b>what of it?</b> It was unknown to the nazirite himself.",
    "<b>And furthermore,</b> consider <b>that which is taught</b> in another <i>baraita</i> (<i>Tosefta</i>, <i>Zavim</i> 2:8): In the case of <b>one who finds a corpse lying</b> across <b>the width of a road,</b> i.e., it had been buried there in such a way that it was impossible for the passerby to avoid becoming impure by passing over the corpse, then <b>with regard to <i>teruma</i>,</b> the passerby is <b>impure.</b> Therefore, if he is a priest, he may not eat <i>teruma</i>. However, <b>with regard to</b> both being <b>a nazirite and</b> being <b>one performing</b> the ritual of <b>the Paschal offering,</b> the passerby is <b>pure. What is different</b> about these situations? <b>Rather,</b> it must be that the <i>halakha</i> of <b>impurity</b> imparted by a grave <b>in the depths is learned as a tradition</b> and not from the verses, which are cited merely in support.",
    "§ The mishna taught that <b>if</b> a nazirite discovered he was ritually impure <b>before he shaved,</b> he negates his naziriteship even if he was rendered impure by impurity of the depths. The Gemara asks: <b>Who</b> is the <i>tanna</i> who <b>taught</b> this opinion? <b>Rabbi Yoḥanan says: It is Rabbi Eliezer, who says</b> that <b>shaving is indispensable</b> to the completion of one’s naziriteship. Consequently, if he discovered he was impure before he shaved, he became impure during his naziriteship, and he negates the period he has observed.",
    "<b>Rami bar Ḥama raised a dilemma: What is</b> the <i>halakha</i> with regard to one who <b>became impure during the full term</b> of the regular days of his naziriteship <b>but</b> his impurity <b>became known to him</b> only <b>after the full term</b> but before he shaved? Perhaps <b>we go</b> according to his <b>knowledge, and it is</b> a case of <b>knowledge after the full term, or</b> perhaps the <i>halakha</i> is <b>not</b> determined by the time of his awareness but by the actual time of the impurity, which occurred during his naziriteship. The Gemara adds: <b>And with regard to what</b> issue was this dilemma raised? It was <b>with regard to</b> his possible <b>negation</b> of the period he observed as a nazirite: Does he negate his naziriteship, or is he considered to have contracted impurity after the completion of his term, in which case he need not start his naziriteship afresh?"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> נָזִיר שֶׁגִּילַּח, וְנוֹדַע לוֹ שֶׁהוּא טָמֵא,",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אִם טוּמְאָה יְדוּעָה — סוֹתֵר, וְאִם טוּמְאַת תְּהוֹם —",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֵינוֹ סוֹתֵר. אִם עַד שֶׁלֹּא גִּילַּח, בֵּין כָּךְ וּבֵין כָּךְ —",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "סוֹתֵר. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>כֵּיצַד? יָרַד לִטְבּוֹל בִּמְעָרָה וְנִמְצָא מֵת",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "צָף עַל פִּי הַמְעָרָה — טָמֵא, נִמְצָא מְשׁוּקָּע",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּקַרְקַע הַמְּעָרָה, <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>יָרַד לְהָקֵר — טָהוֹר. לִיטָּהֵר",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִטּוּמְאַת מֵת — טָמֵא. שֶׁחֶזְקַת טָמֵא — טָמֵא, וְחֶזְקַת טָהוֹר —",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "טָהוֹר, שֶׁרַגְלַיִם לַדָּבָר. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> מְנָא הָנֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִילֵּי? אָמַר רַבִּי אֱלִיעֶזֶר, דְּאָמַר קְרָא: ״וְכִי יָמוּת מֵת",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עָלָיו בְּפֶתַע פִּתְאֹם״, ״עָלָיו״ — בִּמְחֻוֶּורֶת לוֹ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>רֵישׁ",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לָקִישׁ אָמַר: אָמַר קְרָא ״כִּי יִהְיֶה טָמֵא לָנֶפֶשׁ",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹ בְדֶרֶךְ רְחֹקָה״. כִּי דֶרֶךְ: מָה דֶּרֶךְ בְּגִלּוּי, אַף",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כֹּל בְּגִלּוּי. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְאֶלָּא הָדִתְנַן: אֵיזוֹהִי טוּמְאַת הַתְּהוֹם —",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כֹּל שֶׁאֵינוֹ מַכִּירָהּ אֶחָד בְּסוֹף הָעוֹלָם.",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲבָל מַכִּירָהּ אֶחָד בְּסוֹף הָעוֹלָם — אֵין זוֹ טוּמְאַת",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַתְּהוֹם. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>בִּשְׁלָמָא לְמַאן דְּאָמַר כִּי דֶרֶךְ — שַׁפִּיר. אֶלָּא",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְמַאן דְּאָמַר — בִּמְחֻוֶּורֶת לוֹ, כִּי מַכִּירָהּ אֶחָד",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּסוֹף הָעוֹלָם מַאי הָוֵי? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְתוּ, הָא דְּתַנְיָא: הַמּוֹצֵא",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵת מוּשְׁכָּב לְרׇחְבָּהּ שֶׁל דֶּרֶךְ, בִּתְרוּמָה —",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "טָמֵא, בְּנָזִיר וּבַעֲשִׂיַּית פֶּסַח — טָהוֹר. מַאי שְׁנָא?",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֶלָּא טוּמְאַת הַתְּהוֹם גְּמָרָא גְּמִירִי לַהּ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אִם",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עַד שֶׁלֹּא גִּילַּח וְכוּ׳. מַאן תַּנָּא? אָמַר רַבִּי יוֹחָנָן: רַבִּי אֱלִיעֶזֶר",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הִיא, דְּאָמַר: תִּגְלַחַת מְעַכֶּבֶת. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"9\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>בָּעֵי רָמֵי בַּר",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "חָמָא: נִטְמָא בְּתוֹךְ מְלֹאת וְנוֹדַע לוֹ לְאַחַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מְלֹאת, מַהוּ? בָּתַר יְדִיעָה אָזְלִינַן, וִידִיעָה אַחַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מְלֹאת הִיא, אוֹ לָא? וּלְמַאי: לְמִיסְתַּר?",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מַתְנִי׳ נָזִיר שֶׁגִּילַּח</b> תגלחת טהרה ביום שלשים ואחד שלו:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>וְנוֹדַע לוֹ שֶׁהוּא טָמֵא.</b> בטומאת מת בין שנטמא בתוך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מלאת בין שנטמא לאחר מלאת לבו ביום קודם שהביא קרבנותיו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ושגילח: <b>אִם טוּמְאָה יְדוּעָה.</b> היתה בשעה שנטמא ה\"ז סותר את הכל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אבל לא נטמא עד לאחר הבאת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קרבנותיו אפילו בטומאה ידועה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אינו סותר אלא ז' כדתנן בפרק",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שלשה מינין (<a href=\"/nazir/47a\">לעיל נזיר דף מז.</a>) מי שנזרק",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עליו אחד מן הדמים כו' ואוקימנא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בגמרא דלדברי הכל ז' סותר ותו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ואם</span> עַד שֶׁלֹּא גִּילַּח.</b> נודע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לו שנטמא בין בו ביום בין שנטמא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בתוך ימי מלאת: <b>בֵּין כָּךְ וּבֵין כָּךְ.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בין בטומאה ידועה בין בטומאת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:1:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "התהום סותר את הכל: <b>כֵּיצַד.</b> היא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "טומאת התהום שאינו סותר אם נטמא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בטומאת מת וירד לטבול במערה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ביום שביעי שלו ולאחר שיצא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מצא לשם מת שהוא צף על פני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "המים שבפתח המערה והוא לא הכיר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בו כשירד שם לטבול אין זו טומאת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "התהום ואפי' אם לא נודע לו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עד לאחר גילוח ואפילו אם לא ירד",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לשם לטבול אלא להקר ה\"ז טמא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וסותר את הכל: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">אבל</span> אִם <span class=\"dh-divergent\">נמצא</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מְשׁוּקָּע בְּקַרְקַע הַמְּעָרָה.</b> שבשעה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שנכנס לא היה צף בזו יש חילוק",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פעמים שהוא טהור ופעמים שהוא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "טמא כשנכנס לשם ולא נכנס בה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אלא להקר ונודע לו לאחר גילוח",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שנמצא לשם מת משוקע כנגד פי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "המערה ה\"ז טהור דזו היא טומאת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "התהום אבל ירד לשם ליטהר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מטומאת המת ואח\"כ נודע לו ואפילו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לאחר גילוח ה\"ז טמא וסותר את",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הכל אע\"פ שהיא טומאת התהום:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>שֶׁחֶזְקַת טָמֵא טָמֵא</b> העמידו בחזקת טמא: <b>וחזקת</b> <b>טהור.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "יורד לשם בחזקת טהור: <b>שֶׁרַגְלַיִם לַדָּבָר.</b> כלומר שהדברים נראין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:3:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כך דטהור העמד על חזקתו וטמא על חזקתו ותיהוי חזקת טהור",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:3:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "טהור וחזקת טמא טמא: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">גמ&#x27;</span> בִּמְחֻוֶּורֶת לוֹ</b> בברורה לו כגון",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "טומאה ידועה סותר אבל לא על טומאה שאינה ידועה לו: <b>וְתוּ</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">אמר</span> אָמַר <span class=\"dh-divergent\">קרא</span></b> גבי עושה פסח כי יהיה טמא לנפש או בדרך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רחוקה: <b>כִּי דֶרֶךְ <span class=\"dh-divergent\">בגלוי</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">אף</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">טומאה</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">בגלוי</span>.</b> לאפוקי טומאת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "התהום דלא והוא הדין לנזיר דבכל מקום נזיר ועושה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פסח כי הדדי נינהו: <b>בשלמא למ&quot;ד כי דרך.</b> דבגלוי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שפיר דכיון דאחד מכירה בסוף העולם הוי גלוי: <b>אלא למ&quot;ד.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>במחוורת</b> <b>לו</b> <b>כי</b> <b>מכירה</b> <b>אחד</b> <b>בסוף</b> <b>העולם.</b> אמאי הוי טמא והא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אינה מחוורת לו: <b>ותו.</b> בין למ\"ד במחוורת לו בין למ\"ד כי דרך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כיון דמדאורייתא טומאת התהום הותרה גביה הא דתניא המוצא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מת מושכב כו' מאי שנא גבי תרומה דהוי טמא וגבי נזיר ועושה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פסח דהוי טהור: <b>אֶלָּא טוּמְאַת הַתְּהוֹם גְּמָרָא גְּמִירִי לַהּ.</b> דאינה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מטמאה והכי גמירי לה דלנזיר ועושה פסח בלבד אינה מטמאה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:8:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אבל לתרומה לא גמרינן הילכתא ומשום הכי הוי טמא: <b>מַאן</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:9:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>תַּנָּא</b> דאם נודע לו קודם גילוח אע\"פ שהביא קרבנותיו סותר:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:9:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">א&quot;ר</span> יוֹחָנָן: <span class=\"dh-divergent\">ר&quot;א</span> הִיא, דְּאָמַר.</b> בפרק ג' מינין (<a href=\"/nazir/46a\">לעיל נזיר דף מו.</a>) ואחר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:9:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ישתה הנזיר יין אחר מעשים כולן דברי ר\"א דכיון דעדיין לא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:9:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גילח כמי שנודע לו בתוך מלאת דמי וסותר את הכל דאי לרבנן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:9:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כיון שנזרק עליו אחד מן הדמים שוב אינו סותר: <b>בָּעֵי רָמֵי בַּר חָמָא</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>נִטְמָא</b> בטומאת התהום בתוך ימי מלאת ונודע לו לאחר מלאת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:10:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קודם הבאת קרבנותיו וקודם גילוח: <b>מַהוּ? בָּתַר יְדִיעָה אָזְלִינַן.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:10:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כלומר מי אמרינן דהא דגמרינן דטומאת התהום אינה סותרת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:10:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "היכא דידיעה הויא לאחר מלאת אפילו היכא דנטמא בימי מלאת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:10:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "או דילמא כיון דנטמא בימי מלאת אע\"ג דנודע לו לאחר מלאת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:10:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואפילו לאחר הבאת קרבנותיו לא אמרינן דטומאת התהום הותרה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:10:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לו וסותר ולרמי בר חמא דקמיבעיא ליה הכי לא שמיעא ליה מתני'",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:10:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואמטו להכי קמיבעיא ליה הכי אי סותר או אינו סותר כלל:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 63a:10:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    }
  ],
